
As a visitors, I want to search items by category to see a wide variety
As a registered customer, I want to favorite items so that I can I can buy them later
As a customer, I want to contact the seller to get further details about the item
As a user, I want to create an account so that all my activity is saved
As a user, I want to see reviews about a seller so I can trust them


As an administrator, I want to check for real user to manage traffic 
